# Advocate Diary - Legal Case Management System

## Project Overview
Building a production-quality DEMO web application for advocates to manage cases, hearings, clients, and documents with calendar integration and global search.

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: React + Vite + Tailwind CSS + React Router
- **Auth**: Firebase Authentication
- **Backend**: Node.js + Express
- **Database**: Supabase PostgreSQL
- **Calendar**: FullCalendar
- **Search**: Fuse.js

